  <strong>2026-02-19</strong> – <a href="https://github.com/insin/control-panel-for-youtube">control-panel-for-youtube</a> <a href="https://github.com/insin/control-panel-for-youtube/releases/tag/v1.13.4">v1.13.4</a>

  <details><summary>v1.13.4 release notes</summary><p>Visit the <a href="https://soitis.dev/control-panel-for-youtube" rel="nofollow">Control Panel for YouTube website</a> for installation links, more information about the extension, and FAQs (mostly about Safari).</p>

<h2>Changes</h2>
<ul>
<li>Added a workaround for CSS injected by the "Youtube-shorts block" extension breaking loading more videos when we're fixing grid loading placeholders in Home and Subscriptions on desktop</li>
<li>Re-enabled fixing grid loading placeholders in Home and Subscriptions on desktop by default</li>
<li>Hide overlays which would display under the header container when using full size theater mode and hiding the header on desktop</li>
<li>Fixed new Grid items per row Auto +1/+2/+3 settings not working if the options to hide watched &amp; streamed videos and the option to hide channels are all toggled off</li>
<li>Fixed being able to use Vivaldi's Picture in Picture control when using full size theater mode and hiding the header on desktop</li>
<li>Removed hiding Share/Thanks/Clip buttons by default - these will be split into separate options in a future release</li>
</ul>
